"""Modern Chat Interface for Ollama Workbench

This module provides a redesigned chat interface that aligns with the modern design of Open WebUI.
Features:
- Clean, modern chat bubbles
- Floating model selector
- Simplified settings
- Responsive design
- Markdown and code block support
- Tabs for Chat vs Workspace modes
- Prompt suggestion layer
- Advanced thinking features (metacognitive types, agent types, voice types)
- RAG context retrieval functionality
- Session management (save, load, rename)
- Text-to-speech capabilities
- Code block extraction and rendering
- Episodic memory features
- Instance-adaptive CoT prompting
"""

